<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v8" title="Q19_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>
      En un concurso de programación, un equipo recibe 
      <m:math>
        <m:msup>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:msup>
      </m:math>
      puntos por presentarse y 
      <m:math>
        <m:msup>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
        </m:msup>
      </m:math>
      puntos por cada desafío que resuelve. En una ronda en la que resolvió un desafío, se afirma que el equipo obtiene 17 puntos en total.
      ¿Cuál de las siguientes explicaciones justifica correctamente esa afirmación?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        porque 
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        = 0 y 
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        = 8, entonces 0 + 8 = 8 puntos en total.
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En realidad, <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup></m:math> <m:math><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:math> <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup></m:math> <m:math><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:math> <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el total correcto es <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>17</m:mn></m:math>, no 8.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        porque 
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        = 1 y 
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        = 2·2·2·2 = 16, entonces 1 + 16 = 17 puntos en total.
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Se cumple que <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> y también <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math>. Como resolvió un desafío, el total es <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>17</m:mn></m:math> puntos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        porque 
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        = 3 y 
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        = 8, entonces 3 + 8 = 11 puntos en total.
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El valor de <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup></m:math> es <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>. Además, <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup></m:math> vale <m:math><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, porque <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces el total correcto es <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>17</m:mn></m:math>, no 11.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        porque 
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        = 1 y 
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        = 2 + 4 = 6, entonces 1 + 6 = 7 puntos en total.
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Aunque <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> es correcto, <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup></m:math> no significa <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math>. Su valor es <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math>. Por eso, el total es <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>17</m:mn></m:math>, no 7.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los puntajes que se deben sumar</strong></p>
            <p>El equipo recibe <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup></m:math> puntos por presentarse y <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup></m:math> puntos por cada desafío resuelto.</p>
            <p>Como en la ronda resolvió un desafío, el total se calcula sumando una vez ambos puntajes:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup></m:math></strong></p>
            <p>Toda potencia de exponente 0, con base distinta de 0, es igual a 1.</p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular <m:math><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup></m:math></strong></p>
            <p>Una potencia de exponente 4 significa multiplicar la base 2 cuatro veces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Calculando paso a paso:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Sumar los puntajes</strong></p>
            <p>Ahora se suma el puntaje por presentarse y el puntaje por resolver un desafío:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>17</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La afirmación es correcta y la explicación que la justifica correctamente es la <strong>opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            ChoiceB
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            FB_ChoiceB
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            show
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            ChoiceA
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            FB_ChoiceA
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            show
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            ChoiceC
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            FB_ChoiceC
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            show
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            ChoiceD
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            FB_ChoiceD
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            show
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            FB_ChoiceA
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">
            show
          </qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>